*Verujem* da će sutra biti lepo vreme. (I believe that tomorrow will be nice weather.)

*Verovala* sam njemu i bila sam u pravu. (I *believed* him and I was right.)

Nije joj *verovao*, ali je ipak to učinio. (He didn't *believe* her, but he still did it.)

*Veruju* da će biti uspešan. (They *believe* he will be successful.)

Ona ne *veruje* u horoskop. (She doesn't *believe* in horoscope.)